    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines a profile for the Autonomous System Provider Authorization (ASPA) object in the Resource Public Key Infrastructure (RPKI). An ASPA is a digitally signed object that provides a means of validating that a Customer Autonomous System (CAS) has authorized the members of a specified Provider AS set as its upstream provider(s) and/or connected Internet-exchange route server(s).</t>
